race.comment: FINAL MOMENT (2) is a lightly raced filly who won her maiden well here over 1000m last time when backed into $1.65. She should be ready for 1200m now and she'll be hard to hold out with natural upside in what looks a very winnable race. BRUTAL WORLD (5) is another off a smart maiden win, winning well at Bairnsdale from a wide gate. This is harder but she's open to improvement and can measure up. STOLEN ART (3) resumes from a short break. His form last time in was okay for this and he gets the blinkers on from a good draw. EVERY LITTLE THING (6) resumes and is relatively lightly raced. She can improve this time in with minor claims.
